These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, gothic-revival, victorian
There are 4 different nationalities: german, argentine, polish, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: rat, goat, mouse, dog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, comedy, superhero, time-travel
 1. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the rat##1
 3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the polish is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the owner of the dog##2
 8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the german##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the polish and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the egyptian is the victorian house##1
13. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the goat and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| House         | cape-cod  | farmhouse      | gothic-revival   | victorian     |
| Nationality           | argentine | german | polish   | egyptian     |
| Pet   | goat    | mouse         | rat | dog         |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel     | martial-arts     | comedy  | superhero       |

