.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, papaya, zucchini, grapefruit
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dannemann, aristoff, game
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, volleyball, biathlon, cricket
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, freelancer, electrician, lawyer
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the freelancer is between the person eating zucchini and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the lawyer is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the videographer##1
 4. the freelancer is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person eating grapefruit##2
 9. the dannemann-smoker is the person eating grapefruit##1
10. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is the aristoff-smoker##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
13. the electrician is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
